     <h4>Uber Expansion</h4>

<h4>An insight in the Uber mindset</h4>

<p>In this workshop we will tell you more about Uber and the different type of roles we have in our cities and markets. Learn more about running a start-up, expansion, growing a city, supply, marketing, competitors, products, pricing and on demand stunts.</p>

<p>We will then ask you to think with us on a strategic level on a couple of cases and the expansion to new cities. You'll work in small teams to do your research and present your findings.</p>

<p>Workshop will be run by Nicolas Buteau – Recruitment Manager EMEA, Kacper Winiarczyk – Operations Manager Warsaw and Agnieszka Hibbert – Paralegal.</p>
